data.description: Charming 1.5-story home in Springfield, IL! This delightful residence features 2 bedrooms and 1.5 baths, with a master bedroom boasting a cedar-lined closet. Enjoy the spacious fenced yard and the convenience of a detached garage. Located within walking distance from Lincoln Park, this home offers both comfort and accessibility.
